    dc:creator "Pamungkas, Joko" ;
    dc:date "2017" ;
    dc:title "Capitella ambonensis: a new polychaete species (Annelida: Capitellidae) collected from a mangrove habitat on Ambon Island, Indonesia" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306312>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306323>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306318>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306315> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306312>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. A, lateral view from prostomium to 5 th abdominal segment (holotype); B, dorsal view from prostomium to 5 th abdominal segment (holotype); C, genital spines of the paratype MZB. Pol. 00184; D, dorsal appearance of chaetigers 7, 8 and 9 of a female (?) specimen; E, posterior end with pygidium of the paratype MZB. Pol. 0 0 188. Pro, Prostomium; Per, Peristomium; gs, genital spines; Pyg. Pygidium; numbers indicate chaetigers. Scale bars: A – E = 1.0 mm" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/306312/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306323>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. A – D, Scanning electron micrographs of C. ambonensis sp. nov. A, lateral view, chaetigers 4 to 11; B, hooks of the second abdominal notopodia in one fascicle; C – D, hooded hooks of the anterior abdominal neuropodia; E, line drawing of the hooded hook. Scale bars: A = 0.5 mm, B = 15 µm, C – D = 5.0 µm, E = 10 µm. lp, lateral pore." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/306323/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306318>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Methylene blue staining pattern of the holotype. A, lateral view, prostomium to 5 th abdominal segment; B, dorsal view, prostomium to 4 th abdominal segment; C, ventral view, prostomium to 4 th abdominal segment; D, mid-ventral abdomen. Scale bars: A – D = 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/306318/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.306315>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Morphological comparison between C. capitata (A) and C. ambonensis sp. nov. (B). Scale bars: A = 0.5 mm, B = 1.0 mm. A, modified after Blake (2009)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/306315/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

